The required format includes 6 items: property, financing, legal_services, moving_services, setup_services, and total_budget. In the final property solution, all six of these sections are present. Each section is fully detailed according to what is required: 
1) property – includes type, location, and price; 
2) financing – includes solution type, down payment percentage and amount, and mortgage term; 
3) legal_services – includes detailed cost breakdowns; 
4) moving_services – includes service level and cost; 
5) setup_services – includes utility package and estimated cost; 
6) total_budget – includes a complete cost breakdown with all components and a total. Therefore, all items are included and fully specified.

